data.title: Default Password List
data.meta_description: Default Password List - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document lists default passwords for various 3COM network devices, including switches, wireless access points, routers, and firewalls. Many devices have a default username of admin and either a default password of admin, 1234admin, or no password. The document provides notes on privileges and methods of access for each device and password listed.
